lution of this issue, with daily check-ins and escalations as needed. - The blocker poses a significant business risk, potentially impacting $500K in annual recurring revenue from key EU enterprise contracts. Would you like more details on the escalation process or the fallback plans in place?","bullets":[],"sources":[{"id":"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f","url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pcwDpaqMVClET6mfadGy_oCYn4FgigJ-/view?usp=drivesdk","title":"JIRA_INFRA-1247_AWS_EU_Blocker.pdf","sourceId":"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f","sourceType":"drive","sourceTypeLabel":"Drive"}],"citations":[],"answer_text":"Jordan Martinez is responsible for addressing the AWS EU region quota blocker. This issue is critical as it affects the deployment of the Pinecone vector database needed for the AI search project. - Jordan Martinez, the Infrastructure Lead, is managing the resolution of this issue, with daily check-ins and escalations as needed. - The blocker poses a significant business risk, potentially impacting $500K in annual recurring revenue from key EU enterprise contracts. Would you like more details on the escalation process or the fallback plans in place?","sources_used":[{"id":"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f","url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pcwDpaqMVClET6mfadGy_oCYn4FgigJ-/view?usp=drivesdk","title":"JIRA_INFRA-1247_AWS_EU_Blocker.pdf","sourceId":"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f","sourceType":"drive","sourceTypeLabel":"Drive"}],"citationIndexMap":{"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f":1}}},"createdAt":"2026-02-24T09:19:32.529Z"},{"id":"7f87f308-0b5e-4252-ace5-41d19d191ed7","conversationId":"706ca2da-55d9-4479-8b95-eb8218d4a035","role":"user","content":"What's our 2025 product roadmap?","toolCallId":null,"citationsJson":null,"metadataJson":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-24T09:19:43.304Z"},{"id":"6bdf5ec4-4bd4-47cd-9604-f22f2e5c5236","conversationId":"706ca2da-55d9-4479-8b95-eb8218d4a035","role":"assistant","content":"I found some relevant