 Slack, and Jira, enabling natural language queries with a latency of under 2 seconds for 95% of queries [1][3].\n\nWould you like more details on specific metrics or other project-related objectives?","toolCallId":null,"citationsJson":[],"metadataJson":{"response":{"answer":"The Q4 Objectives and Key Results (OKRs) for the AI search project include launching the semantic search feature by November 15, 2024. This involves replacing the existing keyword-based search system with a new semantic search powered by vector embeddings and large language models. The goal is to index over 500,000 documents across various platforms like Google Drive, Confluence, Slack, and Jira, enabling natural language queries with a latency of under 2 seconds for 95% of queries [1][3].\n\n- This involves replacing the existing keyword-based search system with a new semantic search powered by vector embeddings and large language models. [1]\n- The goal is to index over 500,000 documents across various platforms like Google Drive, Confluence, Slack, and Jira, enabling natural language queries with a latency of under 2 seconds for 95% of queries [1][3].\n\nWould you like more details on specific metrics or other project-related objectives?","bullets":[],"sources":[{"id":"82b9fe07-ba26-415c-82ca-41614f25977e","url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OaWf-KzyUEnNp_aUm9dGc9g9scyr-x0n/view?usp=drivesdk","title":"AI_Search_Architecture.pdf","sourceId":"82b9fe07-ba26-415c-82ca-41614f25977e","sourceType":"drive","sourceTypeLabel":"Drive"},{"id":"1602cb5c-021a-4f74-9abc-944fbb22c19e","url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-z6r1IrvdWltGMYOjsUlg6t7A9WU6xt_/view?usp=drivesdk","title":"Product_Roadmap_2025.pdf","sourceId":"1602cb5c-021a-4f74-9abc-944fbb22c19e","sourceType":"drive","sourceTypeLabel":"Drive"},{"id":"d4da6b5b-9916-46cd-ac80-3ae9bc780f71","url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cWDQ4mEaj5ym2QFicMP-AEp4v9yg2qMK/view?usp=drivesdk","title":"Engineering_AllHands_Oct28_2024.pdf","sourceId":"d4da6b